      "text": "さくらは太陽のように明るい笑顔で……\n遙子さんは穏やかで包容力があって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura has a bright smile like the sun…\nHaruko-san is calm and has a gentle presence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は健気で可愛くて……\n雫の茶目っ気が伝わってきて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa is diligent and cute…\nShizuku's mischievousness comes through…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
