      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "それに比べて、私は硬い気がして……こんな表情じゃ\nクールな印象を持たれるのも仕方ないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Compared to that‚ I feel rigid… with this expression.\nIt's no wonder I'm seen as cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺は怜らしくていい表情だと思うが……\nそんなにクールだと思われるのが不満なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that expression suits you‚ Rei…\nAre you unhappy with being seen as cool?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "あ、誤解しないで下さい\n私はクールって言われるのが嫌な訳じゃないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ please don't misunderstand.\nI don't dislike being called cool or cool-looking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "クールとか格好いいとか言われるのは嬉しいんです\n嬉しいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes me happy to be called cool or cool-looking…\nIt makes me happy‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
