      "text": "ただ、私もみんなみたいに明るく可愛く振る舞えたら\n怖いなんて言われることもなかったのかなと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just wonder if I could have avoided being called scary…\nIf I can smile in a cute and bright way‚ just like the others",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "気にしなくても、怜の写真も十分人を引きつける\n魅力があると思うぞ。そうだな……あえて言うなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even without worrying‚ Rei's photo already captivate people.\nI think you have charm. Well… if I were to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "もっと自然な素の笑顔でいられれば\nアイドルとして一段上に行けるかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you could smile more naturally‚\nyou might rise even higher as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
