      "text": "自然な笑顔ですか？　……確かに私はみんなのように\n無邪気に笑えていないかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A natural smile?… It's true that I might not be able to\nlaugh innocently like everyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
